{
  "logNo": "222911338032",
  "title": "[기획] 스토리보딩 작업 Part Ⅱ,  온보딩(Onboarding)",
  "addDate": "2022. 10. 26.",
  "categoryNo": "22",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222911338032",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3384440a-bc41-4b27-a56d-0bcea696b7d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c844af8-1ccd-4fdf-8540-6c1155af6b1e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c0c941b0-beb5-41bf-bfe9-9ebbf466601b\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 29</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-86576a73-cb75-4a3f-8e7b-38bc07f5e03c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-343a83af-d3e4-44b8-a99c-70d857333f09\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1fba8c47-f744-43fa-9b25-e40861290188\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-47c09a28-f881-426b-9005-d19580034970\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-35093d35-c3d1-448b-8b85-7d101b5d32fe\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a164494d-33e5-4979-b5bf-fc9b1660ba6c\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87dafdef-fda6-4225-a9e5-47ae74c2cd5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47f3dab1-34b6-47af-9d66-2f8d3d3ca6c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0fdb104a-dfc2-45cf-8dca-4fa9f5dee7a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>희망은 좋은거죠. 가장 소중한 것이죠. 좋은것은 절대 사라지지 않아요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-471effa4-9708-4ab0-9356-34e5f18570bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-02cc74be-fa69-4266-9d57-d6e60287d94f\" style=\"\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da3a981f-3038-400e-b68c-773014adca2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-19c7f4ad-86eb-4dce-8d5c-78d1eff9e16c\" style=\"\">앤디 듀프레인</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ae8bfe94-d401-4b39-bec4-cc31fd75025a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c35d78d-9acc-436c-aced-143153eb7d01\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-33b95c32-c4e4-49a2-886c-0f7e7c24ad6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:709px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTdfOCAg/MDAxNjY2MDE2ODQxNzAw.MFPetfRtOqhnhNPL2ZtpwJQPxy3mIHCObsRBsGxFTwgg.9d_41_rHel6pNsefPz-V3mzb09OvOCzPZSDPVlEc-iEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w1\", \"originalWidth\" : \"709\", \"originalHeight\" : \"60\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTdfOCAg/MDAxNjY2MDE2ODQxNzAw.MFPetfRtOqhnhNPL2ZtpwJQPxy3mIHCObsRBsGxFTwgg.9d_41_rHel6pNsefPz-V3mzb09OvOCzPZSDPVlEc-iEg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-282ca67f-4b9f-4329-8bb6-919e071ce250\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c72533bc-2db3-4bac-bd28-a35f67f81dd4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d372f25e-0cb6-4e5e-9f88-b3cb53eb6cb0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip1. 위치, 배치에 따른 UI</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-885cca19-6f14-4202-a8d5-01d94da883fb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b2266e86-3c9b-4315-8f6d-6787f5fceea2\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip2. 클릭, 이벤트와 연동</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c3294e0-7887-4b9f-a2f0-a530470b81d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-712d39ed-e108-4786-9ed5-0e2fa2716e3f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip3. 중복과 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f7bc503-e1d6-441d-a754-f1125606cc78\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-669e6dc9-791d-47cd-80fc-8a1fa3987cf8\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip4. 프로세스에 맞는 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d176359c-704e-46d8-8373-c51bb262c1a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-871dee4e-6cf1-4e4b-845a-3214a0e3a32d\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip5. 정확한 전달</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a79e66e-9395-47cf-8488-5ba5ef02a48e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-52ad2fa4-fc22-4baf-97bb-801c7ec7f73e\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f35f756-7420-4d05-b91a-e7c160cba6d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a15d9bea-d97f-4c69-82cb-d094796b7c5d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모바일 UI 구성시 주의사항을 계속해서 올립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90d7b65d-f878-420f-b44b-f30be31db7fd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4058a849-9475-4585-9947-1d05a26f56c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d51a13d2-e0d3-4810-8349-53613ac3fc56\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4f81d71-16e1-491b-bf03-8470703a93d3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d04c0b51-ae9d-49da-8b71-1fca26b40d1e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2583d8c2-5abf-4887-b630-66e469d1ac8f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip4. 프로세스에 맞는 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-59860d25-e8fc-4800-9b29-684eb0774bae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-59860d25-e8fc-4800-9b29-684eb0774bae\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfMTA1/MDAxNjY2Nzg2NjY2NjYy.qibDsq7W_MseTf5GNZg59iUC7f3Pwfcbs3Em_QsNw2Ug.GPahWiXGrzlwm1gEczp6FF6szfMWgLGKZWfd0YeHsGQg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2718\", \"originalHeight\" : \"5006\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfMTA1/MDAxNjY2Nzg2NjY2NjYy.qibDsq7W_MseTf5GNZg59iUC7f3Pwfcbs3Em_QsNw2Ug.GPahWiXGrzlwm1gEczp6FF6szfMWgLGKZWfd0YeHsGQg.PNG.cookthedesign/91%EC%8A%A4%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC%EB%B3%B4%EB%93%9C_%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85_221024.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b4ad355-ea0d-4d2a-95a0-41ea92a16c52\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7903ade3-29ab-4011-9657-3937e4b9fb95\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc3cb31f-a0ed-45b6-bc15-5829164ecc0d\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>온보딩 스토리보드 PPT작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6144c24f-c37c-4ff6-8d49-8d237b47a846\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5da87671-ac18-4afb-b762-be61b07a601a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스토리보드를 기획한 Ⅰ차 내용을 가지고 PPT를 작성해 자세하게 설명해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ecede5a-7221-4d30-a0f9-4ac8a0451e29\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b44afd9e-9bf4-47cd-8d52-7b5beace9103\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스토리보드는 일단 기획과 액션에 따른 프로세스 위주로 작업을 진행하겠습니다. 온보딩의 프로세스는 내가 필요한 인쇄물의 디자인 유형을 먼저 스타일에 따라 선택해서 빠르게 디자인을 제안하는 형식으로 온보딩을 구성하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-8fc75478-6eb9-465f-950c-ac06fcdea943\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d505389a-d86b-41b7-860c-dcd71776a0f7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22aa8170-b429-4a33-a6c1-88634c399208\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f05dce76-680e-4257-a4e0-82d757837627\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">온보딩에서 고객에게 말하고 싶은 것은?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a43f2af8-d2be-4a2b-9f97-090cf52dbc32\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6dfdd7f2-5663-4131-a75f-7b7c806d3a94\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eeed8a26-b927-4b04-9b37-fc7610517774\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-61419ee9-3e3a-48bf-801a-9c366cd042a6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">앱의 취지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6452bd0e-6b53-4e70-b67f-0ffa4e044fb8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-72b127bd-63aa-4d74-9339-db90dfb050e3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">앱의 미리보기 기능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3956119a-c654-4e37-bf0f-5410f3aa1982\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-603eaf65-5f7e-4cc9-855d-98b8aad0033c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">앱은 고객에 대해 알고싶다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a133950a-3f57-4796-be18-7ba02bc41e06\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9afb223e-b6c6-4e60-ae3d-f260d8e62746\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">그리고 앱의 선한 이미지를 먼저 살짝 알려주고 싶다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ad62c94-ec50-4a18-b77a-b1619f03cbb2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-72db4957-5068-4e68-a63c-fbd2369520d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9bf62fec-6750-4116-84a1-9520f1a458d4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2afde466-a1ba-450f-a662-692cd4b52c40\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 4가지 부분에 따라 작업을 해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72192169-4a53-4b93-869a-8cd05480001c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-501ed2f8-c776-45a3-89db-3aca43943b29\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ae84534-5684-46f6-8702-fe337513e5b0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6eb7bebd-bc69-46bb-981b-0a358472692d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 앱은 고객에게 가장 맞는 디자인을 선택하게 해서 가장 빠르고 쉽게 주문하는 사이트를 만드는 목적입니다. 이를 위해 온보딩은 고객이 우리 앱을 먼저 사용해 본 경험이 있는지 또는 고객은 인쇄물을 많이 주문하는 고객인지 그리고 고객이 선호하는 디자인 스타일을 골라 빠르게 추천하는 온보딩을 구현해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5397b75e-0b8f-4aa3-a204-6b1b62744164\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2ce73c03-7ab9-4360-9434-b8e40043c7ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0f636ec9-4ab0-4982-bdaa-ca5d9a3bd3ee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0f636ec9-4ab0-4982-bdaa-ca5d9a3bd3ee\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfNTYg/MDAxNjY2Nzc1ODA4ODUx.jmzp04Zicch2hFxdoYvZooFBFJwCbBDBTYKomZ8Fl9Ig.J2nQczSkQVIuzpaJY3XQ0Qmw_KCqluVnjUn2_t-hXQog.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1280\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1040\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfNTYg/MDAxNjY2Nzc1ODA4ODUx.jmzp04Zicch2hFxdoYvZooFBFJwCbBDBTYKomZ8Fl9Ig.J2nQczSkQVIuzpaJY3XQ0Qmw_KCqluVnjUn2_t-hXQog.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-547b56ef-6701-444f-8c88-dadf6b6dd410\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0b1def01-e61f-4364-8f82-0c80430843cd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-065bcbcd-501e-4737-bd2e-ae8bc8aa2af6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">스플래시를 통해 (주)파파스컴퍼니을 보여준 후 온보딩으로 크게 두가지를 고객에게 물어 볼겁니다. 첫째는 고객의 주문량과 고객의 디자인 스타일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-a9d1cadc-a57e-4043-bfe2-e6e97aa52d30\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-76616945-09c1-4047-b56c-3d2cd5c1aafc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ed88f5c-d961-49ff-944f-47421abcbb71\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5e1db364-4e38-478f-bc22-860fed65a716\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인 스타일 (Design Style)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-619f2e33-1f1c-424d-93ed-24fc57bc40b2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-94af497d-7472-4ea2-8193-3568c22d14fa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">관리자 페이지에서 디자인 이미지를 등록할 때 스타일 구분을 추가하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26774e7f-9eae-4f12-8d4d-24d3c65d354d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4f1e8eb9-2ff7-4a0c-84be-9b20484ea855\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">모던, 스텐다드, 고져스 등 구분을 관리자페이지에 등록하도록 하겠습니다. 이 분류는 조금 더 고민해서 결정하고 개발완료시까지 문서로 정리하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-869661b6-a2aa-4bfa-b0cd-9d4770740318\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a460d0c-26e1-47db-97f6-6f8e36f64dd6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6a460d0c-26e1-47db-97f6-6f8e36f64dd6\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfMjA2/MDAxNjY2Nzc3NTgwNzgz.B-DdD1uphek5PydQ9P82An2AUAkaqHeTLEgiFDIIGoog.uBa_A3AnK1g8qOuDzinkl7lMuLYC-XVgHioASxIafJQg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1280\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1040\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjZfMjA2/MDAxNjY2Nzc3NTgwNzgz.B-DdD1uphek5PydQ9P82An2AUAkaqHeTLEgiFDIIGoog.uBa_A3AnK1g8qOuDzinkl7lMuLYC-XVgHioASxIafJQg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8000c0f0-18c4-4888-960f-c76d17c1bfa2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b35dc63-9734-4100-b05d-ae3bc731bd66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1b79b4fe-b977-488a-ad36-cb5948de4959\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">두번째 페이지입니다. 이 페이지의 의미는 고객의 주문량을 알고 싶은 겁니다. 만약 이 회원의 주문량에 따라 고객응대를 결정하고 싶습니다. 다만 이 시작하기가 끝나면 이 페이지에서 입력한 정보가 고객의 정보까지 연동이 되야 합니다. 이 부분은 개발자와 협의하겠습니다. ppt작성시 중요한 사항이 관리자페이지 연동은 별도로 글씨색이나 굵기를 조정하도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa9c4967-0de6-446d-ac56-fb506369552f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b749bbf8-a567-416a-b13c-2fbf8e835179\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">로그인 전의 정보를 어떤 방법이든 보관하고 그 정보값을 로그인시에 전달할 수 있는지는 가능할듯합니다. 만약 이 전달이 불가능하면 마이페이지에서 추가등록을 통해 추가정보를 받겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-7f2f448a-5f21-4349-845d-13cf9a554977\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31cecb37-e965-442f-ac9c-02558f3da22f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-31cecb37-e965-442f-ac9c-02558f3da22f\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjdfMjEw/MDAxNjY2ODM0ODE3Mzgz.xhv8CW8tK6Ic0M26C0qhkFQ5TDZ0pvaThrUvYU74E7kg.nN8RMCOxHCJSb4yOuckRv_m6TQY5vM6f7S1tdu7726cg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1280\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1040\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMjdfMjEw/MDAxNjY2ODM0ODE3Mzgz.xhv8CW8tK6Ic0M26C0qhkFQ5TDZ0pvaThrUvYU74E7kg.nN8RMCOxHCJSb4yOuckRv_m6TQY5vM6f7S1tdu7726cg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce35c7ed-1b48-408a-90a1-ac4966ede979\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-80ae4169-2324-4b18-9ccf-6b1a10b59615\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a130c6c9-7a27-4318-a6e4-4d40e353febe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">세번째 페이지입니다. 이 페이지의 핵심은 